"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-06-olympic-champions-genuinely-inspiring-netflix-documentary-watched-8-200-000-times-21370643\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team USA gymnastSimone Bileshas dominated at theParis 2024 Olympics, so it's no surprise thatNetflixsubscribers have flocked to watch a documentary about her.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.6973085975809457, \"rank\": 0.29608967683141874, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aftersuffering with a case of 'the twisties'at theTokyo 2020 Olympics, fans of the gymnast were eagerly awaiting her return to the international stage.\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Simone Biles did not disappoint.\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After winning gold in the team event, she became the most decorated American gymnast in Olympic history, going on to win gold in the individual all-round competition and in the vault competition too, and picking up a silver medal in the floor competition.\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 418, \"end\": 426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9897447844345184, \"rank\": 0.010361455458910698, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Biles' journey has not been easy.\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She made the difficult decision topull out of the Tokyo Games in 2020, in order to prioritise her mental health.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The new Netflix documentary,Simone Biles Rising, charts her mental health journey as she balances her personal life with a return to training ahead of Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5609859074049003e-15, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}, {\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8390566260977528e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wake up to find news on your TV shows in your inbox every morning with Metro's TV Newsletter.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1002, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_show\", \"score\": 0.9990656361880147, \"rank\": 0.0007733702174439028, \"text\": \"TV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_show\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_show\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up to our newsletterand then select your show in the link we will send you so we can get TV news tailored to you.\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's tugged on viewers' heartstrings, with Livie sharing on X: 'Four minutes into Simone Biles' Netflix series and I am already so emotional.'\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1220, \"end\": 1232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another shared: 'I am not even halfway thru episode 1 of Simone Biles: Rising documentary on Netflix, and I am in tears'.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5609859074049003e-15, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The critics were impressed by the documentary too, rating it a perfect 100% on review aggregator site Rotten Tomatoes.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1507, \"end\": 1522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rotten_Tomatoes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rotten Tomatoes\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rotten_Tomatoes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rotten_Tomatoes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anmar Kalia, writing for the Observer, said: 'Packed as it is with jaw-dropping slow-motion footage of Biles's vaults and leaps, it's impossible to come away from Rising without rooting for this astounding woman, who has dominated her sport for a decade.'\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anmar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anmar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anmar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anmar\"}, {\"begin\": 1531, \"end\": 1536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.578612033148332e-14, \"text\": \"Kalia\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kalya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Robert Lloyd of the Los Angeles Times calls it 'A genuinely inspiring two-part documentary.'\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Lloyd_(bass)\", \"score\": 0.4273712031787774, \"rank\": 0.6912162162160294, \"text\": \"Robert Lloyd\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Lloyd_(bass)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Lloyd_(bass)\"}, {\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.357853922475309e-37, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's no surprise, then, that Simone Biles Rising has been watched a whopping 8.2 million times since it was released.\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 2004, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"First landing on Netflix on July 17, the two episodes picked up 4.7 million views in just four days, debuting at number three on the streamer's most-watched chart.\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2023, \"end\": 2030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5609859074049003e-15, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The following week, the documentary was watched 3.5 million times, dropping down to number four on the list.\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But with two more episodes expected to air in the autumn - which will presumably focus on Biles' experience at the Paris Olympics - it's unlikely that this is the last we have seen of Simone Biles Rising in the Netflix chart.\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2492, \"end\": 2499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5609859074049003e-15, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elsewhere on the list,Cobra Kai: Season 6 has topped the chartfor the second week in a row, with an enormous 9.5 million views.\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Karate Kid spin-off is set 34 years after the 1984 film and looks at the events from the perspective of Johnny Lawrence, as well as following his decision to reopen the titular karate dojo.\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2745, \"end\": 2760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Lawrence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8387687096713275e-15, \"text\": \"Johnny Lawrence\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Lawrence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johnny_Lawrence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A new entry comes in second place this week: Dirty Pop received 5.6 million views after first landing on Netflix on July 24.\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2937, \"end\": 2944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5609859074049003e-15, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Struggling with thinning or dull hair?\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 2996, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Experts say the real issue starts at your scalp  Mother's Day gifts for new mums and mums\\u2011to\\u2011be under \\u00a